casebody.data:
No. 10-8367 (10A698). Leroy White, Petitioner v. Grantt Culliver, Warden, et al. 562 U.S. 1174, 131 S. Ct. 992,

178 L. Ed. 2d 820,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 611. January 13, 2011.

Application for stay of execution of sentence of death, presented to Justice Thomas, and by him referred to the Court, denied. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Supreme Court of Alabama denied. The order heretofore entered by Justice Thomas is vacated.

Same case below, 408 Fed. Appx. 292.
